'''Aïcha Macky''' (8 Mutarama 1982), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Nigeri|Nigeriya]] ndetse na sociologue .  Azwi cyane nkumuyobozi wa documentaire''[[:en:The_Fruitless_Tree|The Fruitless Tree]]''.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 8 Mutarama 1982. Igihe yari afite imyaka itanu, nyina yapfuye amaze kubyara.  Yabonye impamyabumenyi ya Master I muri Audiovisual and Creative Documentary muri Institut de Formation aux Techniques de l'Information et de la Communication (Training Institute for Information and Communication Technologies: IFTIC) muri [[Nigeriya]] nyuma arangiza icyiciro cya kabiri cya Master II muri Sociology no muri Gukora Film documentaire muri Kaminuza ya Gaston Berger muri [[Senegali|Sénégal]] muri 2013. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu mwaka wa 2011, Macky yerekanye bwa mbere bugufi ''Moi et ma maigreur'' yari yerekeranye n'imyumvire yoroheje y'abatuye [[Nigeriya]]. Amaze gutsinda bwa mbere, yakoze bwa kabiri bugufi bwa ''Savoir faire le lit'', butera kwibaza ku makimbirane hagati y'ababyeyi n'abakobwa bo muri [[Nigeriya]] ku bijyanye n'uburere bw'imibonano mpuzabitsina. Mu mwaka wa 2016, yakoze filime ye ya mbere yerekana filime ''L'Arbre sans imbuto'' yibanze ku rugamba rw’umugore ufite ubugumba, guhuza ubuzima bwe.  Iyi filime yarashimiwe kandi yegukana ibihembo birenga 50 mu birori ku isi. Nyuma yaje kugurwa mbere numuyoboro wa NHK wu [[Buyapani]].   Muri Kamena 2016, filime yatsindiye igihembo cya documentaire muri Afrika Movie Academy Awards (AMAA). 

Usibye gukora firime, ni n'umwarimu w'abarimu muri sinema igendanwa. Ayobora abakiri bato kuzamura ireme muri firime ngufi zivuga ku makimbirane nyayo mu bihugu bihana imbibi nka [[Nijeriya]], [[Libiya]], [[Kameruni]], [[Burukina Faso|Burkina]] Faso na [[Mali]]. Yatsindiye igihembo cya Alumni of Young African Leaders Initiative (YALI), iyi ikaba ari gahunda y'Abanyamerika yatangijwe n'uwahoze ari perezida [[Barack Obama]] . Nyuma yaje guhabwa izina rya Ordre des Arts et des Lettres na minisitiri w’umuco wa Repubulika [[Ubufaransa|y’Ubufaransa]] kubera ubwitange yagize mu mibereho myiza y’abaturage ba [[Nigeriya]] na sinema. 

Macky yazamuwe mu ntera ya Knight of Academic Palms yo muri Repubulika ya [[Nigeriya]] hanyuma Knight of Arts. Yakoze kandi nka Ambasaderi-wagenwe na Oasis Niger incubator center ishinzwe kongerera ubushobozi abagore n’abakobwa. Hagati aho, ni umwe mu bagize komite mpuzamahanga ishinzwe umurage wa sinema nyafurika (CPCA). 

